### 2.1 插入排序
**排序问题描述**

输入:n个数的一个序列{a1,a2,..,an} <br>
输出:输入序列的一个排列{a1',a2',..,an'},满足a1'<= a2'<=..<=an'.

**算法描述**
```
INSERTION-SORT(A)
1 for j = 2 to A.length
2     key = A[j]
3     //Insert A[j] into the sorted sequence A[1..j-1]
4     i = j - 1
5     while i > 0 and A[i] > key
6         A[i+1] = A[i]
7         i = i - 1
8     A[i+1] = key

```
**算法实现**
```java
public int[] insertionSort(int[] A){
        for(int j = 1; j < A.length; j++){
                int key = A[j];
                int i = j - 1;
                while(i>0 && A[i] > key){
                        A[i+1] = A[i];
                        i--;
                }
                A[i+1] = key;
        }
        return A;
}
```

